              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Google your target keywords, list the top-ranking directories and platforms in your niche, then claim, optimise, and populate your profile on each. Focus on the top three to five platforms per keyword rather than every listing site you can find.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">Is barnacle SEO worth the investment?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>For local businesses and new sites without domain authority, yes. It captures qualified traffic while you build your own rankings. For dominant brands with strong SEO, it is a supplementary tactic rather than a primary channel.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">How long before I see results from barnacle SEO?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Because the host site already ranks, results can appear within days of publishing your profile. Full impact usually shows in 30 to 90 days as reviews accumulate and Google indexes the enriched profile.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
