              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Local SEO optimises your own presence (Google Business Profile, citations, on-site local pages). Barnacle SEO adds a layer of borrowed rankings from third-party platforms like Yelp, TripAdvisor, or industry directories that already rank for your target keywords.</p></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>

